# PhotogrammetrySession.Output.skippedSample(id:)

**Case**

The type of element used for Object Capture updates. The [doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/PhotogrammetrySample] with the [doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/PhotogrammetrySample/id] indicated was not able to be used for reconstruction.

## Declaration

```swift
case skippedSample(id: Int)
```

## Monitoring data ingestion

- **PhotogrammetrySession.Output.invalidSample(id:reason:)**: A provided sample was invalid.
- **PhotogrammetrySession.Output.automaticDownsampling**: The session reduced the image size because of memory constraints.
